  "title": "ART TEACHER (PART TIME)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description &amp; Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>• Prepare and teach art classes to children age 3 to 12 years old. (e.g. Acrylic painting, oil painting, watercolour, sketching, oil pastel, clay, etc.)<br>\n• Teach Fine Art to children age 10 to 12 years old.<br>\n• Design and develop art curriculum and lesson plans<br>\n• Create positive and vibrant classroom environment that is conducive for learning<br>\n• Guide the student effectively to achieve learning outcomes in the curriculum, while tracking progress and providing timely feedback.<br>\n• Monitor the progress of each child and cultivate their interests and confidence in learning art.</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>• Possess art background and certification.<br>\n• Experience in art curriculum development will be an added advantage.<br>\n• Passionate about art and enjoy working with children.<br>\n• Positive, cheerful, responsible and resourceful.<br>\n• Self-motivated with initiative, able to work independently and as a team.<br>\n• Able to travel across Singapore on assignment.</p>",
